{"tid":1534611,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"深圳白石洲小朋友冇書讀","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:47:10.000Z","uid":242083,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a818390ac84f03af0b4018222c8118157afcbe09","tid":1534611,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"事源<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ui2FQDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUi2FQDM.jpg&h=deafd2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁之後小朋友就冇書讀了<br />\n有人喺we7 po左一輯圖，design得好好，防審查兼有縮圖排版，有埋煽情故事清楚訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/knwjmLT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FknwjmLT.jpg&h=4d34f2da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內容［長］<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/exkwcSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexkwcSL.jpg&h=3cd36061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tskPJZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtskPJZF.jpg&h=012b1a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pGf0QEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpGf0QEM.jpg&h=e0616e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wz6fEyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWz6fEyf.jpg&h=e6b110ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzCyrdn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzCyrdn.jpg&h=b25bbde2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkUpxTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkUpxTs.jpg&h=f8c26a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wh7KxTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWh7KxTx.jpg&h=63c5c2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7LcGM0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7LcGM0.jpg&h=8cc0cace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiWbXkp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiWbXkp.jpg&h=66adc028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74a553370813e9cadac4b8ff562c167451e142c6","tid":1534611,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f17d4f3cbd21c83e0c9265c58c3e1136fac5a6c","tid":1534611,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"885bdf65513912694d1b56f747fb1b3b86264bfc","tid":1534611,"uid":92515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"唔讀書 咪可以做護旗手囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc84d8c235455b9215717092e041eeff31fe4c1c","tid":1534611,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"ab44b51bd43e5b77129acc5071f0e50e73b288f5","tid":1534611,"uid":65790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"去過親身睇過<br />\n<br />\n不過只可以講一句&quot;關我撚事?&quot;"},{"pid":"c38d44887000a0a9f310d99b635b31287dfe73ba","tid":1534611,"uid":78241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"自己都未顧得掂"},{"pid":"697197b1b0865a7bd4d29fd3a637f5254ac07f56","tid":1534611,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"愛國愛黨 黨的恩情比天高<br />\n<br />\n有黨可以唔返學架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee2e78cce55183c290bcb6de8f78dfef971794b","tid":1534611,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab44b51bd43e5b77129acc5071f0e50e73b288f5","tid":1534611,"uid":65790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"去過親身睇過<br />\n<br />\n不過只可以講一句&quot;關我撚事?&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:21:26.000Z","msg":"中國咁大 其他省廢架？？"},{"pid":"acb9a88a0bbc098ccb35ea2d3d6f685cace4d66e","tid":1534611,"uid":144883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 關我撚事 </span></span>"},{"pid":"c2b1817286f8f2b43063d9505302af5642355997","tid":1534611,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:38.000Z","msg":"贏国咁強大點會小朋友無書讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i